高位回落后，印度卢比可能小幅上涨。打印。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 02:50:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-may-find-breathing-space-dollar-retreats-two-year-peak-2024-12-23/</guid></item><item><title>越南将于2025年底开始修建连接中国的新铁路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vietnam-start-construction-new-railway-linking-with-china-by-end-2025-2024-12-23/</link><description>越南总理范明正表示，越南将于明年年底开始修建一条从其北部最大港口到中国边境的新铁路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 01:14:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vietnam-start-construction-new-railway-linking-with-china-by-end-2025-2024-12-23/</guid></item><item><title>支撑！ 2025年全球经济风险叠加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/brace-risks-stack-up-global-economy-2025-2024-12-23/</link><description>特朗普潜在的关税和全球冲突带来了不确定性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 01:12:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/brace-risks-stack-up-global-economy-2025-2024-12-23/</guid></item><item><title>以入侵为背景的台湾电视剧《零日》的制作者担心来自中国的强烈反对</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/makers-taiwans-zero-day-tv-series-set-around-invasion-fear-backlash-china-2024-12-23/</link><description>一架中国战机在台湾附近失踪。随着台湾进入战备状态，中国派遣大量军舰和飞机进行封锁。台北街头一片恐慌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 01:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/makers-taiwans-zero-day-tv-series-set-around-invasion-fear-backlash-china-2024-12-23/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市和风险资产为美国通胀缓解欢呼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-23/</link><description>亚洲股市周一上涨，此前美国通胀的良好数据恢复了明年进一步宽松政策的希望，同时华盛顿避免了政府关门也让人们松了口气。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 00:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-23/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示，将 TikTok 在美国保留一段时间可能值得</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-says-it-could-be-worth-keeping-tiktok-us-little-while-2024-12-22/</link><description>该应用程序将于 1 月 19 日在美国面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 19:31:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-says-it-could-be-worth-keeping-tiktok-us-little-while-2024-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国就维吾尔族、西藏问题对加拿大机构和个人采取措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-take-steps-against-canada-institutions-individuals-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-22/</link><description>这些措施包括冻结资产和禁止入境。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 09:53:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-take-steps-against-canada-institutions-individuals-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国称台湾为“红线”，批评美国对台湾的新军事援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-taiwan-red-line-criticises-new-us-military-aid-island-2024-12-22/</link><description>中国周日批评美国对台新的军事援助，称这一5.71亿美元的援助计划严重违反“一个中国原则”和中美联合公报的规定</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 03:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-taiwan-red-line-criticises-new-us-military-aid-island-2024-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>与波罗的海电缆泄露有关的中国船只恢复航行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-ship-linked-baltic-sea-cable-breach-resumes-voyage-2024-12-21/</link><description>瑞典海岸警卫队周六表示，一艘因波罗的海两根光纤电缆破裂而接受调查的中国散货船在附近丹麦航道上停泊一个多月后再次开始航行。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 15:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-ship-linked-baltic-sea-cable-breach-resumes-voyage-2024-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>拜登批准向台湾提供5.71亿美元的国防支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-approves-571-mln-defense-support-taiwan-2024-12-21/</link><description>白宫表示，美国总统乔·拜登周五同意向台湾提供 5.713 亿美元的国防支持，同时国务院批准向台湾出售价值 2.65 亿美元的军事装备。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 05:39:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-approves-571-mln-defense-support-taiwan-2024-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>当局称，七名中国公民在美国试射导弹时试图非法进入关岛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/seven-chinese-nationals-tried-illegally-enter-guam-us-tested-missile-authorities-2024-12-21/</link><description>关岛海关检疫局表示，在美国导弹防御局使用新型雷达进行关键导弹拦截试验期间，七名中国公民因非法进入关岛而被捕。</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 03:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/seven-chinese-nationals-tried-illegally-enter-guam-us-tested-missile-authorities-2024-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国称其宇航员完成了创纪录的太空行走</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-says-its-astronauts-complete-record-breaking-spacewalk-2024-12-20/</link><description>根据中国载人航天工程局的一份声明，两名中国宇航员本周完成了超过九个小时的太空行走世界纪录，标志着北京迅速扩张的太空计划的又一个里程碑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 20:33:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-says-its-astronauts-complete-record-breaking-spacewalk-2024-12-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>